---
import Layout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Cookies">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-8">Cookies</h1>

    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">Last updated: 26/03/2026</p>

    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      This website is designed to be simple, fast, and privacy‑friendly. I do not use cookies for tracking, advertising, or personal data
      collection.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-10 mb-4">1. Essential Cookies</h2>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      This website does not use any essential cookies. You can browse the site without any cookies being stored on your device.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-10 mb-4">2. Analytics</h2>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      I use Plausible Analytics to understand general website traffic. Plausible is a privacy‑focused, cookie‑free analytics tool. It does
      not use cookies, does not track you across the web, and does not collect personal data.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-10 mb-4">3. Third‑Party Cookies</h2>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      This website does not use any third‑party cookies, advertising cookies, or tracking pixels.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-10 mb-4">4. Managing Cookies</h2>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
      Because this website does not use cookies, there is nothing you need to manage or disable. You can browse freely without any tracking
      or cookie consent banners.
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-semibold text-xl mt-10 mb-4">5. Contact</h2>
    <p class="text-dark/70 leading-relaxed">
      If you have any questions about this Cookies Policy, you can contact me at:
      <strong>hello@penninedigital.co.uk</strong>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
